item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - USHER (Dolby Atmos) [Apple Music Exclusives] + 2 Additional Albums & 1 Song
item.description:
Since nobody has made the request for it, these albums by USHER are in Atmos on Apple Music, but 360 on Tidal & Amazon.

My Way (25th Anniversary Edition)
8701
Confessions (Expanded Edition)
Raymond v Raymond (Expanded Edition)
Versus
COMING HOME (Feb 11th.)

There are also a bunch of singles too, but the albums are the most important. Also, these 2 albums are Apple Music exclusive now.

Too Good To Be True - Rick Ross & Meek Mill
Welcome 2 Collegrove - 2 Chainz & Lil Wayne

And the song "Rush Hour" by Crush & J-Hope is still in Atmos in the China region for Apple Music.

Thank You!
